      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really wonderful shape! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next adventure right away. It's the perfect balance of quality and value. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
