    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride in ownership, offering a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior finish maintains a brilliant shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free. The leather upholstery remains soft and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All technological features, including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is top-tier; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a thick folder of receipts to prove it. The engine idling is whisper-quiet, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. Recently fitted with premium tires and fresh brake pads, this car needs nothing but a new driver. It comes complete with two master keys, the original owner's manual, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
